{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1778778097.563693", "card_id": "Q_2038210796468098494", "card_label": {"type": "boiling", "icon": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a8ec286ae756c2ab8377774b27f8ebc7_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-022e7c409e51515f784aa70403aef8d4_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1238}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中美元首举行会谈，有哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 14 日上午，国家主席习近平在北京人民大会堂同来华进行国事访问的美国总统特朗普举行会谈。 习近平强调，中美之间的共同利益大于分歧，中美各自成功是彼此的机遇，中美关系稳定是世界的利好。双方应当做伙伴而不是对手，相互成就、共同繁荣，走出一条新时代大国正确相处之道。我期待着同特朗普总统就事关两国和世界的重大问题交换意见，共同为中美关系这艘大船领好航、掌好舵，让 2026 年成为中美关系继往开来的历史性、标志性年份。习近平：让 2026 年成为中美关系继往开来的历史性、标志性年份 - 中新网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-4ca1c5af83b9e16072486c2ae8087e7a.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "4218 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038210796468098494"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExOTUwMTA5MSCa85TQBjAAOKAZQAByEzIwMzgyMTA3OTY0NjgwOTg0OTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1778778097.564831", "card_id": "Q_2038333650341557719", "card_label": {"type": "boiling", "icon": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a8ec286ae756c2ab8377774b27f8ebc7_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-022e7c409e51515f784aa70403aef8d4_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 297}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "特朗普访华欢迎宴会，都有哪些看点值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": " "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d82b009a54c146b0b0ab93506f180ebd_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3320 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038333650341557719"}}, "a