": {"text": "有网友发现一个现象，如果「中国风」很重的图，或者有一些类似「游戏」、「原画」、「BlingBling 感」、「幻想」（就是偏魔幻色彩或者描述一个梦境大概的这种描述）这种就很容易出现这种所谓的「碎渣感」，虽然可能有时候一眼看不出来，但是你去看其他的图再返回来看就会有这种感觉。反而越是真实感系列的图，或者纯文本或者截图类的，就完全没有这种感觉。 被 OpenAI 图像生成核心大佬陈博远 私信回复「正在加班修复这个问题」。吐槽 GPT 新模型碎渣感，没想到 OpenAI 的大佬回复了 之前在 GPT Image 团队的研究科学家陈博远 @MIT 奶茶店长在知乎分享的「我在 OpenAI 修中文」的评论区，也有答主提过此问题。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-962b4ad0c2cc802b5115b6917fd6eeef_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037211734738301895"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExOTQ2NjU5NyCnrobQBjAAOGFAEXITMjAzNzIxMTczNDczODMwMTg5NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1778778097.572719", "card_id": "Q_3161823405", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 188}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么在极地大乱斗经常看见出肉的小法？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c885c271cf0edb1a5c0e3496a9ba6e1d_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3161823405"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExMTYwODkyNiDY96S5BjAAOMUBQBJyCjMxNjE4MjM0MDV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1778778097.572979", "card_id": "Q_2036793015952467043", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 74}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "武磊已经代表国足出场 99 场，国足是否应该再用武磊一次，让武磊完成百场记录，风风光光告别国足？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "怎么说呢，国足在今年 6 月份和新加坡还有泰国有两场热身赛，现在网上也很多球迷说，国足应该在 6 月份的热身赛带上武磊，让武磊完成他国足一百场出场记录。 那么武磊已经 34 岁，而且他伤病不断，如今武磊的状态其实是不适合国家队的，可是这件事说来也巧了，武磊之前已经代表国足出场 99 场，就差一场就到了一百场。 所以有球迷心疼武磊，他们说明年的亚洲杯正赛，国足可以不带武磊，可是在国足的热身赛，应该让武磊有个体面的国足告别仪式，到时候国足安排武磊代表国足踢最后一场，完成武磊的国足百场记录。 而且到时候还要把武磊的家人，也就是武磊的妻子和孩子都请来，包括武磊的恩师徐根宝都要到场，大家热热闹闹的庆祝武磊的国足百场记录，让武磊风风光光的告别国足，给武磊最大的尊重。 而且这种国脚替国家队告别赛，在别的国家也有先例，这也是一种足球文化，以人为本。 不过也有人不支持，他们认为武磊实力不够进国足了，那么就不能给武磊开这个后门，国足的热身赛对于国足很重要，这是国足考察各位国脚状态，排兵布阵的关键时刻，国足还要备战明年的亚洲杯，国足比赛可不是武磊的个人表演赛。 那么就事论事，武磊代表国足出场 99 场，国足是否该再用武磊一次，让武磊完成一百场记录，也就是最后一舞，让他风风光光的告别国足呢"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-df947fd37128a5ba6f6182b8fd8eb993_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2036793015952467043"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExOTQ1MjA2NiCwooDQBjAAOH1AE3ITMjAzNjc5MzAxNTk1MjQ2NzA0M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1778778097.573749", "card_id": "Q_2037438839103426671", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 269}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "女子花 1880 元办不限次数瑜伽季卡，连上 20 多天被教练踢出群聊，此举是否合理？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "女子花 1880 元办不限次数的瑜伽季卡，连上 20 多天课后被教练踢出群聊：天天来，你不累吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e6f4a21edae4ae46aac8c0d52586a7b6.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037438839103426671"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExOTQ3MjUzMiCp1YnQBjAAOPkFQBRyEzIwMzc0Mzg4MzkxMDM0MjY2NzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1778778097.574093", "card_id": "Q_2037573368195409221", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 38}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待《给阿嬷的情书》赞助商中大部分是潮汕本地的餐饮小店？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "随着电影《给阿嬷的情书》口碑出圈，片尾那一串赞助商名单也引起了网友关注。放在其他电影，赞助商可以是押宝的「资本」，但对于《给阿嬷的情书》来说，这些更多是雪中送炭的朋友。 在《给阿嬷的情书》官方合作伙伴中，多为潮汕小微商家，如仅 3 家分店的「南海冰室」、牛肉火锅店「陈记顺和」等。部分品牌坦言仅提供少量物资或未实际投资，如汕头本土奶茶品牌「一杯潮茶」在电影路演期间提供 100 杯奶茶及冰箱贴作为赞助，未投入现金。导演则以免费电影票回赠，被调侃为「最划算的赞助交易」。 除了本地餐饮，也有几个稍有名气的「可心柔」「真功夫」被网友无情定性为「怀疑赞助的是盒饭」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2365051e74b9891930db30409aae14df.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037573368195409221"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExOTQ3OTkwNyDzz4vQBjAAOJkBQBVyEzIwMzc1NzMzNjgxOTU0MDkyMjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1778778097.574787", "card_id": "Q_2033490095815272316", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "四川人说的吃「mang mang 」到底啥意思？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "那个四川人小时候都听到过大人说吃 mang mang 了，但是有没有人解释的清楚到底啥意思，吃奶这么说，吃饭也这么说，实在太好奇了！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d90f39998ff793c7c6d69b00679e4a6b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2033490095815272316"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExOTM0Njg2MSCbmtDPBjAAODVAFnITMjAzMzQ5MDA5NTgxNTI3MjMxNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1778778097.575293", "card_id": "Q_2038039004210259865", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 243}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "武汉大学正式取消进校预约制，持身份证即可入校，此举会带来哪些影响？大学校园到底该怎么「敞开」才合适？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 13 日，武汉大学正式取消社会公众进校预约制度。公众无需任何预约，仅凭本人身份证即可在珞珈门、弘毅门步行入校，工作日及节假日均开放。这意味着学校自 2023 年 7 月实施的预约入校模式全面结束。公众进入武汉大学已无需预约，带上身份证即可进校"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b51b6045fb11b68ca41fe7bd5034f4e1_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2038039004210259865"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExOTQ5NzM5NyCbs5LQBjAAOMYDQBdyEzIwMzgwMzkwMDQyMTAyNTk4NjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1778778097.575790", "card_id": "Q_2036685548291617157", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人到中年，如何去注重自已的身心健康？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "人到中年，规律作息管住嘴迈开腿，静心少忧、看淡得失，养护身心安稳度日。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5f7e0332229c49833ab84de17dfb9a76.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2036685548291617157"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExOTQ0NzM5MiCa2v7PBjAAOJcBQBhyEzIwMzY2ODU1NDgyOTE2MTcxNTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1778778097.576117", "card_id": "Q_534707325", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么几百年的小提琴音质很通透？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-1d3e7488315753e64c96d39388f887e4.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/534707325"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Is+GxkPago8oeEAMaCDgxMTA1NzQ4IIT1vZQGMAA4SEAZcgk1MzQ3MDczMjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1778778097.576361", "card_id": "Q_13659081112", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "装修中，不能省钱图便宜的是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "装修中以下几个方面不能省钱图便宜： 水电材料 • 水管：若使用劣质水管，容易出现漏水、爆裂等问题，后期维修不仅麻烦，还会给家居造成严重损失。 • 电线：质量差的电线绝缘性能不佳，易引发短路、火灾等安全事故，危及生命财产安全。 防水材料 • 卫生间、厨房、阳台等经常接触水的区域，防水至关重要。劣质防水材料防水效果差，易导致渗漏，影响邻里关系，还会使墙面、地面受潮发霉、损坏。 基础五金件 • 合页、铰链：承担着门窗、家具柜门的开合功能，质量差的合页、铰链易生锈、断裂，导致门窗、柜门开关不顺畅甚至无法正常使用。 • 门锁：关系到家庭安全，便宜的门锁防盗性能低，易被撬开，存在极大安全隐患。 墙面乳胶漆 • 劣质乳胶漆环保性不达标，会释放大量甲醛、苯等有害物质，长期危害人体健康。而且其遮盖力、耐擦洗性差，墙面容易出现变色、掉粉等问题。 地板 • 质量差的地板甲醛含量可能超标，同时耐磨性、抗压性不足，使用一段时间后会出现划痕、变形、空鼓等问题，影响美观和使用寿命。 定制家具板材 • 定制家具若采用劣质板材，同样会有甲醛释放量超标的问题，还可能结构不稳定，容易出现变形、开裂等情况，影响家具的使用功能和寿命。 总之，装修中涉及安全、环保和基础功能的部分不能为了省钱而选择便宜的材料，否则可能会带来诸多隐患和后期高额的维修成本。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-1751a219cfd87481f4bebf2aefd46862_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/13659081112"}}, "attached_info": "CkIIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExMzcwNzIwMyD184W+BjAAOJkBQBpyCzEzNjU5MDgxMTEyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1778778097.577317", "card_id": "Q_2035205756237108368", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 74}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "假如有一种生物，本身有剧毒，吃了会很快被毒死，导致没人敢碰它，这种生物能笑到最后吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "注意是生物本身有剧毒。不是说它会分泌毒素之类的那种，是它本身有毒。吃它就等于在吃毒药，是不是没人会吃了？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-93f2b4e610c5ec12b8ccbe0f1568459e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2035205756237108368"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExOTM5NjU2NiDwlenPBjAAOJABQBtyEzIwMzUyMDU3NTYyMzcxMDgzNjh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1778778097.577593", "card_id": "Q_2037841145099703846", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "墨脱支教的表妹 2 块钱就能买到包邮的发圈，你收到过最离谱的包邮商品是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "表妹这件事让我真正认识到了拼多多偏远地区包邮的实力，以前我一直觉得买贵 = 买对，但逐渐发现其实购物是有很多选择的，想听听大家分享一些在拼多多买到过什么特别惊喜，超出预期的东西呀！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-32d37e3d414bf46b7b9ba6eff571293e.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037841145099703846"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExOTQ4NzU0MCDWwo/QBjAAOGJAHHITMjAzNzg0MTE0NTA5OTcwMzg0NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1778778097.577867", "card_id": "Q_2031930574454137517", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待在哈佛大学物理学教授 Schwartz 指导下，Claude 完成高能物理论文？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "论文地址：Resummation of the C-Parameter Sudakov Shoulder Using Effective Field Theory 研究经过（原文）：研究经过（译文）：人工智能最终会代替数学家或理论物理学家吗？ 在这篇论文中，Claude 提出了一种新的分解定理。用教授的话说，在理论物理里，这种定理并不多，每一个都会让我们对量子场论的理解更深一层，而且它做出了可以被实验检验的物理预测。 原本需要教授做几个月的项目在 AI 搬砖下只用了两周。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-95cdce001724fe1d086f5370f3258429_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2031930574454137517"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIs+GxkPago8oeEAMaCTExOTI5NDQ2MiCwwbnPBjAAOPMBQB1yEzIwMzE5MzA1NzQ0NTQxMzc1MTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3gA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "